---
---

<section id="about" class="py-28 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section label -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="section-label"><span class="gold-line"></span>About</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <!-- Left: text -->
      <div class="space-y-5 text-[#AAAAAA] text-base leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          I'm a <span class="text-[#E8E8E8] font-medium">Technical Lead at L'Oréal</span>, working on cloud
          platforms, data systems, and modern engineering solutions on Google Cloud Platform. My day-to-day sits at
          the intersection of data engineering, cloud architecture, and software development.
        </p>
        <p>
          My journey began in 2018 at <span class="text-[#E8E8E8]">Accenture</span> as an Associate Software
          Engineer. Over the years I've moved through TCS, Wipro, and L'Oréal — learning something valuable at
          every stage, from Azure pipelines and PySpark to GCP, FastAPI, and React.
        </p>
        <p>
          What excites me most isn't a specific technology. It's the
          <span class="text-gold-400 font-medium">process of learning, improving, and solving problems</span>.
          That mindset led me naturally into trading — where markets are one of the most honest feedback systems
          in the world, constantly challenging assumptions and rewarding discipline.
        </p>
        <p>
          Both worlds — technology and markets — reward structured thinking, require continuous learning, and
          remind us that certainty is often an illusion.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: stat cards -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="card p-5">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-gold-400 mb-1">8+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-muted">Years of experience</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-5">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-gold-400 mb-1">4</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-muted">Companies</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-5">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-gold-400 mb-1">GCP</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-muted">Primary cloud</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-5">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-gold-400 mb-1">∞</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-muted">Learning in progress</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Philosophy card spanning full width -->
        <div class="card p-5 col-span-2 border-gold-400/20 bg-surface-800">
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-gold-400 mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">Philosophy</div>
          <p class="text-[#E8E8E8] text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Growth is rarely the result of a single breakthrough. More often, it's the result of
            <span class="text-gold-400">small improvements compounded consistently over years.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
